<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Telecom Connectivity>
We are investigating telecom provider connectivity issues in the US-EAST-1 Region affecting calls for some customers.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Telecom Connectivity>
Between 3:49 AM and 7:56 AM PST we experienced telecom provider connectivity issues in the US-EAST-1 Region affecting calls for some customers. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
